name: The Voids
description: The Voids are a NFT rock band formed in Some Nowhere in 2021. The group, whose line-up comprise Trevor Nothing, Garry Noneman, Aleister Whateverly, David Myth and Pyotr Pustota, are regarded as the most influential band of all time. They are integral  to the development of Aquarius era's overculture and popular music's recognition as an art form. The band explored music styles ranging from no-wave and musique concrete to noise rock and future psychedelia. As pioneers in contemporary recording, songwriting and artistic presentation, The Voids revolutionised many aspects of the music industry. Shh, do you hear nothing?
